===Anda tezga-d===

Mezwara d aḥric n tuddar deg tɣiwant n Ukfadu deg twilayt n [[Bgayet]] seg assegwas n 1984. Tezga-d deg wedrar n [[Aẓru n Taɣaṭ|Weẓru n Taɣaṭ]]. Ad naf deg tmurt-is [[Tasift n Rmila]] i yideggren deg [[Asif n Summam|Wasif n Summam]]

===Tilisa===

Mezwara tela tilisa akwed tuddar-nni : 

*Deg wegmuḍ ɣer taddart n [[At Ɛelwan]]
*Deg wenẓul ɣer taddart n [[Tawrirt]] ed taddart n [[Ilmaten]]
*Deg umalu ɣer tuddar n [[Tagruja]] ed [[Imeɣdasen]] 
*[[Tiẓgi n Wekfadu]] af ugafa

